This '''[[Blaster rifle/Legends|blaster rifle]]''' was in operation during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and used by the [[Viidaav (species)|native warriors]] of [[Viidaav]]. The gray-hued weapon had a long, wide [[Barrel/Legends|barrel]] and a shoulder mount.

These [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]] were used in combat against [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] during the [[Battle of Viidaav]]. They proved to be a match for the [[Cloning/Legends|clones]]' [[DC-15A blaster rifle/Legends|DC-15A blaster rifles]].

